landing.noapp: ʻAʻole pono ʻoe i kahi polokalamu e hoʻohana ai iā {{ BRAND }} ma kāu kelepona a i ʻole papa! Hana maikaʻi ka pūnaewele pūnaewele ma ke kelepona.
landing.intro: ʻO {{BRAND}} ({{TRANSLITERATION}}) kahi ala maikaʻi e ʻike ai i nā hoaaloha hou. Ke hoʻohana ʻoe iā {{ BRAND }}, koho mākou i kahi mea ʻē aʻe a ʻae iā ʻoe e kamaʻilio hoʻokahi a me kekahi. No ke kōkua ʻana iā ʻoe e noho palekana, ʻaʻohe inoa ke kamaʻilio ʻana ke ʻole ʻoe e haʻi i kekahi ʻo ʻoe (ʻaʻole ʻōlelo ʻia!), a hiki iā ʻoe ke hoʻōki i ke kamaʻilio ʻana i kēlā me kēia manawa. E ʻike i kā mākou <6>Nā ʻōlelo a me nā kūlana</6>, a me <8>Nā alakaʻi kaiaulu</8> no ka ʻike e pili ana i nā hana a me nā hana ʻole i ka hoʻohana ʻana iā {{ BRAND }}. {{ BRAND }} Ua hoʻololi ʻia ke kamaʻilio wikiō ma AI akā ʻaʻohe kūpono kūpono. Na nā mea hoʻohana wale nō ke kuleana no kā lākou hana i ka wā e hoʻohana ana iā {{ BRAND }}
landing.disclaimer: <0>Pono ʻoe he 18 (a i ʻole ka hapa nui o ke kānāwai ma kou mana) a ʻoi paha e hoʻohana iā {{BRAND}}</0>. E nānā i kā {{BRAND}} <4> ʻŌlelo a me nā kumu </4> no ka ʻike hou aku. Hiki ke loa'a ka 'ike hou aku ma <6>https://www.connectsafely.org/controls</6> a me nā paena 'ē a'e.
landing.pleaseleave: E ʻoluʻolu, e haʻalele iā Lamdazle a e kipa i kahi kahua kanaka makua inā ʻo ia ka mea āu e ʻimi nei a he 18 ʻoe (a i ʻole ka hapa nui o ke kānāwai i kou mana) a ʻoi paha.
landing.termscheck: Ma ka nānā ʻana i ka pahu e ʻae ana ʻoe ua nānā ʻoe i kahi ʻae e hoʻopaʻa ʻia e {{BRAND}} <3>Nā Kūlana a me nā kumu</3>, <5>Kulekele pilikino</5> a me <7>Nā alakaʻi kaiaulu</7>.
landing.agecheck: ʻAʻole hiki iā ʻoe ke hoʻohana i kēia lawelawe inā ʻoe ma lalo o ka makahiki 18 a i ʻole ka makahiki o ka hapa nui o ke kānāwai i kou mana. E ʻike i kā mākou <1>Nā ʻōlelo a me nā kūlana</1> no ka ʻike hou aku. <3>Ma ka nānā ʻana i ka pahu e hōʻoia a hōʻike ana ʻoe he 18 mau makahiki ʻoe (a i ʻole ka hapa nui o ke kānāwai i kou mana) a ʻoi paha.</3>

error.disableadblocker: <0> Manaʻolana mākou e hauʻoli ana ʻoe i kā mākou pūnaewele. I mea e hoʻomau ai i ka hoʻohana ʻana, makemake mākou e noi iā ʻoe e hoʻopau i kāu adblocker. Ua noa ka hoʻohana ʻana i kā mākou pūnaewele, a ʻo nā hoʻolaha i hōʻike ʻia ma kā mākou pūnaewele e kōkua iā mākou e uku i nā kumukūʻai o ka lawelawe ʻana.
